snippet.title: WB's "Happy Birthday Amber Heard" Tweet Confirms She's in Aquaman 2?
snippet.description:
WB's "Happy Birthday Amber Heard" Tweet Confirms She's in Aquaman 2?

Yesterday was Amber Heard's birthday, and WB's official Aquaman twitter account congratulated her online, much to the dismay of many of her haters.

It's a sign of good faith, so does that mean she's staying in Aquaman 2 or not?

Hard to say, but we don't know that WB was ever going to get rid of her to begin with, despite the controversy surrounding her.

I discuss in this video, so check it out.
